| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2585 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c0b19311-2bcc-5b4c-8056-a9d1d75d525e"
